s\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/two-before-maghrib\/","url_meta":{"origin":12952,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Two raka&#8217;at of recommended prayer before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the caller to prayer announced the prayer, people among the companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would stand and proceed to the pillars of the mosque until the Prophet came out to them. Thus, they would pray two cycles before sunset\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/11\/hypocrites-if-they-knew-crawl\/","url_meta":{"origin":12952,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: They would crawl to prayer if they knew","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"No prayer is more burdensome to the hypocrites than the dawn and evening prayers. If they knew the blessing in them, they would come even if they had to crawl.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 657, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 651 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25408,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/11\/three-regular-practices\/","url_meta":{"origin":12952,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Worship: The Prophet advises three practices","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: My dear friend the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, advised me to do three deeds and I will never abandon them until I die: to fast three days of every month, to perform forenoon prayer, and to sleep after performing the Witr prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33619,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/sunan-maghrib-if-you-wish\/","url_meta":{"origin":12952,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recommended two raka&#8217;at before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Muzanni reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPray before the sunset prayer.\u201d The Prophet said on the third time, \u201cFor whomever wishes,\u201d as he disliked for people to consider it an obligatory tradition. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1183 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/